{"tid":1733013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[粟一燒特約廣告] 要令一隻鱷魚放口，係要揸佢春袋，唔係要擘大佢個口","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:12:45.000Z","uid":190579,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"045599bcb279b8786bcb2987a2806166e7c7aaf3","tid":1733013,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n不要燒狗宿<br />\n不要燒高官屋企<br />\n不要燒政府大樓</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">現實1: </span></ins><br />\n警犬絕對有足夠武力強攻poly<br />\n琴晚成晚都唔攻係因為唔想攻<br />\n唔係攻唔入<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n現實2:</span></ins><br />\n警犬佈放夠密夠深<br />\n我方要極高武力先可以攻破<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>現實3:</ins></span><br />\n我方大部分人番緊工... <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(唔好屌住啦屌嚟冇用)</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推論:</span></ins><br />\n警犬主戰略係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>圍城缺一</strong></span>，誘poly手足突圍再拘捕<br />\n副戰略係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">圍點打援</span></strong>，拘捕油尖旺既援兵<br />\n主力攻poly解圍難度極高，容易被捕<br />\n<br />\n警犬相信我方精銳盡在poly，所以poly係第一目標<br />\n警犬精銳都盡在poly<br />\n我方必須<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直擊警犬痛處</span></strong><br />\n令佢地覺得攻poly既得益 少於 痛處被打既傷害<br />\n咁佢地先會調派兵力離開poly<br />\npoly先有機會解圍<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n不要燒狗宿<br />\n不要燒高官屋企<br />\n不要燒政府大樓</div></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f178b9be8d84f83b2477e2947e802cb1a89e54d7","tid":1733013,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5f3c9b8035dcc9b726f89e2c90e8a3f8582841b4","tid":1733013,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"